<br>
You get one freebie. When Derakor spawns (either respawn or at server up) he spawns *without* pets. The first time he gets aggroed, he'll spawn pets the first chance he gets. If he's running, he won't spawn them. If he's hitting you, he won't spawn them. If he hits the icewall and has to run through it, he'll damn sure spawn them. If your monk aggros him and feigns, he spawns them. Level 1 jackass in another guild runs in there and suicides on him, he spawns them. I don't know why this is, but it is.<br>
<br>
Other than that phenomena, I would say the chances of monks getting a single vindi pull are pretty slim. The best bet if you're not willing to fight all 3 at once is to split the pets off first using the icewall delayed warping technique (Vindicator is taller, thus faster, therefore he warps back through the wall about half a second before his pets do). Once they're dead, they're dead for something like 30 minutes. <p><a target="new" href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=11554">Dagny Blazestorm <Arete></a><BR>
