<br>
However, whenever we need to pull vindi now, we just grab the pets at same time and put an SK or pally with high hp on them to tank them, and kill off the pets while MT is building aggro on vindi. Gives ya a little something to do while waiting for the assist call. And its also a lot better than waiting for the monk(s) to get a &quot;clean pull&quot;. <p><hr width=100%>
